div1.p: United States District Court for the Western District of Washington.
Albert F. In the Matter of Albert H. Young et al for a writ of Habeas Corpus } No. 2628 Praecipe.
To the Clerk of the above Entitle Court:

You will please issue subpoena due term on behalf of above named petitioners returned on Tuesday Dec. 16 1913 at 1913 to Henry M. White Court of Immigration & Thos M. Fritz to bring all records, letter of files, & cocounsel sent to Seer of Labor in the Deportation proceeding against above named petitioners; or copies thereof of orginial are not in your possesion. }RW McClelland Hap Meyer W.L. Meyers W.L. Johurch atty for petitioner
Notice. - Attorneys will please endorse their own Filings Rule 11.
United States District Court Western District of Washington
Filed in the U.S. District Court, Western Division of Washington Northern Division Dec 15 1913 Frank L. Crosby, Clerk, By EML Deputy
